OL,5, A woman who used virtual reality to    
OL,6, understand her child's visual          
OL,7, impairment says seeing the world       
OL,8, through her daughter's eyes is "mind   
OL,9, blowing".                              
OL,11,FCaroline Henderson's daughter Aibhilin,
OL,12,Fseven, was diagnosed with ocular       
OL,13,Falbinism and nystagmus at 11 weeks old.
OL,15,FWhen Caroline and her husband Carl used
OL,16,Fa VR headset developed in Belfast, they
OL,17,Fsaid it was "overwhelming".            
OL,19,FIt showed them just how frustrating her
OL,20,Fvisual impairment was for Aibhilin.    
